<h2><a name="GetStarted" id="GetStarted"></a>Get Started</h2>
<p>This is the starting point for creating Data Management Plans and requesting</p>
<p><a name="DMPResearch-Initiated" id="DMPResearch-Initiated"></a><img src="/Content/Images/instructions/DMP.jpg" width="332" height="33" alt="DMP Research-Initiated" /></p>
<ol>
  <li>Select &quot;Data Management Plan for Research-Initiated Project&quot; on the <em>Get Started</em> page.</li>
  <li>Click Next after you read the <em>Intorduction</em> page.</li>
  <li>Enter research project information on the Project Details page.</li>
  <li>click Save and Next.</li>
</ol>
<p>Using existing Data Management Plan as a template:</p>
<ul>
  <li>If there are existing Data Management Plans then you will be able to see the <em>Data Management Plan Template</em> page.</li>
  <li>If you wish to use an existing Data Management Plan as a template then select Yes and select the approapriate project.</li>
  <li>If you do not wish to use an existing Data Management Plan as a template then select No.</li>
  <li>Click Save and Proceed to DMP</li>
</ul>
<p>Proceeding with the Data Management Plan:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Enter the relevant information in<em> section 1: Information About Research Data</em> page.</li>
  <li>Click Save and Next.</li>
  <li>Enter the relevant information in<em> section 2: Data documentation and organisation</em> page.</li>
  <li>Click Save and Next.</li>
  <li>Enter the relevant information in<em> section 3: Ethics, confidentiality and privacy</em> page.</li>
  <li>Click Save and Next.</li>
  <li>Enter the relevant information in<em> section 4: Data Storage and Backup</em> page.</li>
  <li>Click Save and Next.</li>
  <li>Enter the relevant information in<em> section 5: Deposit and Long-Term Preservation</em> page.</li>
  <li>Click Save and Next.</li>
  <li>To gain access to a Project Storage Space confirm the request by selecting &quot;I acknowledge that.....&quot; and clicking Submit.</li>
  <li>You will see <em>Confirmation</em> page.</li>
  <li>You will also receive a confirmation email.</li>
</ol>
<p>You will also receive an email containing link to your  Project Storage Space once it has been created.</p>
<p><a href="#Top">[Back to top]</a></p>
